\ls1\ilvl0\cf2 {\listtext	\'95	}{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://www.foodterms.com/encyclopedia/dash/index.html"}}{\fldrslt Dash}}\cf0  of hot sauce\
{\listtext	\'95	}1 pound lump crab or crab claw meat, picked over\
